pageTitle: Itinerary for Friday, January 25, 2019 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Quebec City, Quebec

12:30 p.m. The Prime Minister will deliver remarks at a luncheon hosted by the Chambre de commerce et d’industrie de Québec, and participate in a Q&A.

Ballroom
Hilton Québec
1100, boulevard René-Lévesque Est

Notes for media:

    • Open coverage
    • Media are asked to arrive to the lobby no later than 11:45 a.m.

3:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will visit with members of the Quebec City Muslim community at the Centre culturel islamique de Québec.

Closed to media.
